{"tid":1617533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美商務部宣布 將對中國44億美元木櫥櫃加稅","createTime":"2019-10-03T23:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:12.000Z","uid":314178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b68768404ed75a894fa3f1b546e3e8d5ffebf511","tid":1617533,"uid":314178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:24:22.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕今年8月美國商務部初步裁定，將要求美國海關及邊境保衛局（CBP），對從中國進口的木櫥櫃及梳妝台收取現金保證金，如今又有新的進展，美國商務部宣布，中國木櫥櫃進口商恐面臨最高251.6％的稅額。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部3日宣布對中國木櫥櫃、梳妝台反傾銷調查的初步裁定，認定中國出口商傾銷利潤幅度為4.49％至262.18％，美國商務部將指示美國海關與邊境保護局收取現金保證金，美國商務部指出，2018年中國進口木櫥櫃價值約為44億美元（約新台幣1367億元），請願單位為美國廚櫃聯盟，牽涉企業則包括大連美森木業、日照富凱木業、安心廚家具等，稅額為28.7％到251.6％。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部計畫於明年2月17日做出最終裁定，並由美國國際貿易委員會於3月30日做出裁決。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n美國商務部宣布，中國木櫥櫃進口商恐面臨最高251.6％的稅額。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2935755\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2935755&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=5a11b7bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2935755&h=153e7f4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2935755</a>"},{"pid":"cef93ee3c491f6b00e50fce9ef71eb3f196da798","tid":1617533,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:43:04.000Z","msg":"唔好畀淋病spin走！！！錯重點！！！<br />\n萬一正苦真係用緊急法推蒙面法，焦點應放在緊急法！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1617518/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1617518/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bce7c2d77bc06429f818e8f8ae10bd50ecefe04f","tid":1617533,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa